**Recursive task spawning:**

```cpp
void recursive_task(ThreadPool& pool, int depth) {
    if (depth == 0) return;

    pool.submit(recursive_task, std::ref(pool), depth - 1);
    pool.submit(recursive_task, std::ref(pool), depth - 1);
